Summary: To other in AZ Yes here we come! Take a look at these 2 nights worth of images
divs: Sighting DetailsOk these are just two nights worth of unknowns in the airspace over Phoenix AZ. Thank you Mr. Goverenment Debunker for you have inspired me to post as many Unknowns as I can get or find or film. May God and the Angels be with you as they are with me! This part one as many more parts will follow in the weeks to come. Amazing how many different craft we are seeing over this area. There must be a welcome to Earth station nearby! Smile and be happy!
